job_tasks.phrase: Execute demonstrations, POCs, and evaluations through coordination of the physical and human resources of Dataiku and the customer; lead the combined team to carry out the agreed upon course of action to prove that Dataiku delivers the needed value better than our competitors
job_tasks.justification: This phrase describes coordinating resources, leading teams, and demonstrating value against competitors, which aligns with understanding and translating business needs into technical solutions and proving business value.

job_tasks.phrase: Answer questions and provide technical guidance to the customer's technical team regarding the demonstrated or evaluated solutions
job_tasks.justification: Providing technical guidance to customers in the context of demonstrations and evaluations relates to understanding customer needs and ensuring the solution meets them.

job_tasks.phrase: Assist in sales pipeline building activities including attendance at live and/or virtual trade-shows and industry conferences, working with marketing and or partners on campaign design and execution and other activities specified by sales and pre-sales management
job_tasks.justification: This involves supporting sales and marketing efforts, which are inherently business-focused activities aimed at generating revenue and market presence.

job_tasks.phrase: Provide regular updates on your activities to support accurate regional forecasting
job_tasks.justification: Providing updates for forecasting directly relates to business operations and planning.

job_tasks.phrase: participate in continuous development activities that expand or build on your knowledge and skills with new product releases, GTM programs and initiatives & relevant enablement sessions
job_tasks.justification: Engaging with Go-To-Market (GTM) programs and product releases, and participating in enablement sessions, indicates an involvement in understanding and promoting business initiatives.

job_tasks.phrase: participate in departmental activities like GTM or SE offsites.
job_tasks.justification: Participation in departmental and GTM offsites further solidifies the business-centric nature of the role.

classification.rationale: This job description heavily focuses on business understanding, sales support, customer demonstrations, and business development activities. It lacks any mention of core AI/ML tasks like model building, data engineering, or specific AI technologies, making it not relevant to the GenAI Engineer or ML Engineer profiles.
